 160:indcpa.c      **** /*************************************************
 161:indcpa.c      **** * Name:        gen_matrix
 162:indcpa.c      **** *
 163:indcpa.c      **** * Description: Deterministically generate matrix A (or the transpose of A)
 164:indcpa.c      **** *              from a seed. Entries of the matrix are polynomials that look
 165:indcpa.c      **** *              uniformly random. Performs rejection sampling on output of
 166:indcpa.c      **** *              a XOF
 167:indcpa.c      **** *
 168:indcpa.c      **** * Arguments:   - polyvec *a:          pointer to ouptput matrix A
 169:indcpa.c      **** *              - const uint8_t *seed: pointer to input seed
 170:indcpa.c      **** *              - int transposed:      boolean deciding whether A or A^T
 171:indcpa.c      **** *                                     is generated
 172:indcpa.c      **** **************************************************/
